      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just so quiet here. i keep waking up and for a split second i forget... and then it hits me all over again. the house is just so empty. i don't even know why i'm bothering with getting up or making coffee or anything. nothing feels real anymore. it's like i'm just a ghost walking around a life that doesn't belong to me.",
