      "content": "sometimes i look at the empty side of the bed and i just think... maybe it wouldn't be so bad to just stop. not even in a scary way, just... to stop fighting this weight. it feels like i'm just dragging around a body that doesn't have a reason to be here anymore. does that even make sense? that it feels more natural to just let go than to keep forcing myself through these days?",
